title: Expansion panel
---
p.-text
  | Expansion panels are components designed to be folded and stacked one over the other. It has three states: active,
  | pending and done. When it is pending, only the title is shown, when it is active, it unfolds to show its content,
  | and when it is in state done, only some information is shown to the user. Two classes represent this three states:
  | <code>-done</code> is for done, <code>-active</code> is for active and no class for pending state.

